data.description: Enjoy all Coon Rapids has to offer while living in this great pocket of homes around the corner from Riverview Park. This three level residence features original hardwood floors, 3 bedrooms on one level, enormous concrete patio and large fenced in yard. Home is located 2 blocks from the Mississippi River Trail (MRT) which leads to Coon Rapids Dam Regional Park. Here you can take the path across the river or enjoy many outdoor activities like renting kayaks, biking, hiking, playing volleyball, listening to one of the free outdoor concerts in the summertime or even trout fishing at Cenaiko Lake. Conveniently located minutes from historic downtown Anoka and Riverdale where you will find an abundance of great shops and restaurants. Come and explore this amazing opportunity today!
